WEBVTT

00:01.000 --> 00:04.587
♪♪

00:04.671 --> 00:07.132
♪ We are The Fungies ♪

00:07.215 --> 00:10.510
♪ Prehistoric fungi
in a mushroom to-o-wn ♪

00:10.593 --> 00:11.928
♪ Outside, we look different ♪

00:12.011 --> 00:13.555
♪ Inside, we're the same ♪
Yeah!

00:13.638 --> 00:16.057
♪ Everyone's a Fungie
in their own way ♪

00:16.141 --> 00:18.393
♪ Come join The Fungies ♪

00:18.476 --> 00:21.730
♪ Explore a brand-new world
made just for yo-o-u ♪

00:21.813 --> 00:23.398
♪ If you're inclusive,
inquisitive ♪

00:23.481 --> 00:24.983
♪ Respectful, and kind ♪

00:25.066 --> 00:28.570
♪ You can be a Fungie, too ♪

00:28.653 --> 00:31.573
[ Spooky music plays ]

00:31.656 --> 00:34.909
♪♪

00:34.993 --> 00:37.078
Seth, at the
3-point line.

00:37.162 --> 00:39.581
At the buzzer!

00:39.664 --> 00:40.999
Rejected!

00:41.082 --> 00:42.167
And, now, Claudette

00:42.250 --> 00:45.253
with the big 3
from downtow-ow-n!

00:45.336 --> 00:46.755
Ha!
[ Sproing! ]
[ Buzzer ]

00:46.838 --> 00:48.590
[ Crowd cheering ]
Oh, yeah! Fungies win!

00:48.673 --> 00:49.591
Whoo-hoo!

00:49.674 --> 00:52.051
[ Laughter ]
Yeah! Yeah!

00:52.135 --> 00:53.803
C'mon, kids.

00:53.887 --> 00:55.638
Who cleans all this?

00:55.722 --> 00:58.057
Mr. Mergley, that's who.

00:58.141 --> 01:00.935
That's 'cause cleaning up
is your job, Mr. Mergley.

01:01.019 --> 01:03.354
A job you're not
very good at.

01:03.438 --> 01:05.356
I'm tryin', y'know?

01:05.440 --> 01:07.650
You kids are so messy.

01:07.734 --> 01:09.819
Yeah, well, school is
for learning,

01:09.903 --> 01:11.196
not cleaning.

01:11.279 --> 01:13.490
We could be<i> less</i> messy.

01:13.573 --> 01:15.200
Let's clean
our lockers.

01:15.283 --> 01:16.576
Yeah!

01:16.659 --> 01:18.620
Where to start...

01:18.703 --> 01:19.954
Hmm...

01:20.038 --> 01:21.039
All better.

01:21.122 --> 01:22.791
Oh, puh-leez!

01:22.874 --> 01:24.167
[ Clang ]

01:24.250 --> 01:25.293
[ Whistle! ]
[ Gasp ]

01:25.376 --> 01:26.503
That, right there?

01:26.586 --> 01:28.671
A grade-A messy locker.

01:28.755 --> 01:31.633
Ew! It's making
my eyes water.

01:31.716 --> 01:33.927
Seth, you're such
a little piggy.

01:34.010 --> 01:34.886
Who, me?

01:34.969 --> 01:35.929
[ Laughs ]
[ Sproing! ]

01:36.012 --> 01:37.472
[ Oinking ]

01:37.555 --> 01:38.973
[ Laughter ]

01:39.057 --> 01:40.016
[ Bell rings ]

01:40.099 --> 01:41.810
School time.

01:41.893 --> 01:42.977
Wow, Seth's locker

01:43.061 --> 01:44.103
Hold it.
is so gross.

01:44.187 --> 01:45.480
No class until you

01:45.563 --> 01:46.981
clean up this mess!

01:47.065 --> 01:49.984
What?! You haven't
the authority.

01:50.068 --> 01:51.361
Actually, I do.

01:51.444 --> 01:53.655
The principal gave me
this special coupon

01:53.738 --> 01:54.948
for my birthday.

01:55.031 --> 01:57.867
"Punishment of 1 child"?
[ Gasp ]

01:57.951 --> 02:00.453
And I'm using it
on<i> you.</i>

02:00.537 --> 02:01.871
Start scrubbin'.

02:03.581 --> 02:05.208
Ooh...
All: Busted!

02:05.291 --> 02:07.460
[ Laughter ]

02:07.544 --> 02:11.256
There's gotta be an easy way
to deal with this.

02:11.339 --> 02:13.174
Hmm...

02:13.258 --> 02:15.009
[ Hissing ]

02:15.093 --> 02:17.178
♪♪

02:17.262 --> 02:18.972
Yep, smells clean to me.

02:19.055 --> 02:21.599
You can't just spray
the mess away.

02:21.683 --> 02:22.767
Ya gotta get in there

02:22.851 --> 02:24.519
and scrub
like you mean it.

02:24.602 --> 02:25.603
Ughhhh!

02:25.687 --> 02:28.314
I want this
locker spotless.

02:28.398 --> 02:29.691
Clean, schmean!

02:29.774 --> 02:30.775
I just wish this mess

02:30.859 --> 02:32.569
would take care
of itself!

02:32.652 --> 02:34.362
Your wish is
my command.

02:34.445 --> 02:35.738
Commander Beefy!

02:35.822 --> 02:37.198
I've come to help,
Seth.

02:37.282 --> 02:38.950
Well, technically it's part
of my court-ordered therapy,

02:39.033 --> 02:40.368
you know, make right
with those I've wronged,

02:40.451 --> 02:41.786
blah, blah, blah.
Anywho,

02:41.870 --> 02:43.830
so you want this mess
to take care of itself?

02:43.913 --> 02:46.207
Why, you just need
a little space powder.

02:46.291 --> 02:47.709
♪♪

02:47.792 --> 02:49.627
[ Twinkle! ]

02:49.711 --> 02:51.588
[ Laughing ]

02:51.671 --> 02:56.759
♪♪

02:56.843 --> 02:58.428
[ Wailing ]

02:58.511 --> 03:00.221
[ Screeching ]

03:03.099 --> 03:04.183
[ Running footsteps
clanging ]

03:04.267 --> 03:06.728
You're welcome.

03:06.811 --> 03:08.021
[ Thunder rumbles ]

03:08.104 --> 03:09.439
[ Snoring ]

03:09.522 --> 03:11.441
Hey, guys.
What'd I miss?

03:11.524 --> 03:12.984
It's quiet
reading time.

03:13.067 --> 03:14.319
You clean
your locker?

03:14.402 --> 03:17.864
Let's just say the mess
took care of itself.

03:17.947 --> 03:19.073
You three, shh!

03:19.157 --> 03:21.409
[ Whispering ]
Quiet reading time.

03:21.492 --> 03:22.577
[ Lightning strikes ]

03:22.660 --> 03:24.579
[ Murmuring ]
Aah!

03:24.662 --> 03:26.623
Okay, calm down.

03:26.706 --> 03:28.041
I will investigate.

03:28.124 --> 03:29.417
Creature:
[ Roar ]

03:29.500 --> 03:31.711
-Aah!
-It's scary!

03:31.794 --> 03:32.921
On second thought...

03:33.004 --> 03:34.672
Seth, Claudette,
Cool James,

03:34.756 --> 03:35.882
you go check,

03:35.965 --> 03:39.636
as, uh, punishment
for talking.

03:39.719 --> 03:43.222
Yep, everything seems to be
in order, so far.

03:43.306 --> 03:44.891
Guess we can turn
around now.

03:44.974 --> 03:48.728
Wow! Mr. Mergley
worked really hard.

03:48.811 --> 03:50.772
Well, looks like
he's got it covered.

03:50.855 --> 03:51.814
Let's go.

03:51.898 --> 03:53.107
[ Both sniffing ]

03:53.191 --> 03:54.609
Did you cut one,
Seth?

03:54.692 --> 03:56.110
♪♪

03:56.194 --> 03:57.278
[ Gasp ]

03:57.362 --> 03:59.113
There!

03:59.197 --> 04:00.448
[ Roar ]

04:00.531 --> 04:02.951
Garbage monster!

04:03.034 --> 04:04.452
Aah! Aah!

04:04.535 --> 04:05.453
[ Roar ]

04:05.536 --> 04:07.705
-Whoa
-[ Crying out ]

04:07.789 --> 04:09.082
[ Clang ]
[ Roar ]

04:09.165 --> 04:10.750
To the classroom!

04:10.833 --> 04:12.085
[ Roar ]

04:12.168 --> 04:13.419
Seth:
Aah! Aah!

04:13.503 --> 04:14.545
[ Slam ]

04:14.629 --> 04:16.297
No!
Kids!

04:16.381 --> 04:17.423
[ Rattling ]
The door!

04:17.507 --> 04:18.675
[ Roaring ]

04:18.758 --> 04:20.677
Aah!

04:20.760 --> 04:22.595
[ Panting ]

04:22.679 --> 04:24.013
I hate this.

04:24.097 --> 04:25.139
What do we do?!

04:25.223 --> 04:26.808
Psst!
Over here!

04:26.891 --> 04:28.393
[ Growl ]

04:28.476 --> 04:29.852
[ Slam ]

04:29.936 --> 04:31.104
[ Growling ]

04:31.187 --> 04:36.317
♪♪

04:36.401 --> 04:37.777
[ Grumble ]

04:37.860 --> 04:39.320
♪♪

04:39.404 --> 04:41.823
[ Sigh ]
That was close!

04:41.906 --> 04:44.867
Where'd that monster
even come from?

04:44.951 --> 04:46.327
What? Why are you
lookin' at me?

04:46.411 --> 04:48.121
I don't know!
I mean, who --

04:48.204 --> 04:49.580
who could know?
Not me.

04:49.664 --> 04:54.335
This is every custodian's
worst nightmare.

04:54.419 --> 04:56.921
A mess monster
that feeds on messes,

04:57.005 --> 04:59.340
growing stronger
with every mess!

04:59.424 --> 05:03.428
Luckily, I've prepared
for this exact scenario.

05:03.511 --> 05:05.847
Been savin' up supplies
for<i> years.</i>

05:05.930 --> 05:08.182
Glass cleaner,
mold scrubber.

05:08.266 --> 05:09.517
We need
to clean this beast

05:09.600 --> 05:11.519
before it trashes
the whole school!

05:11.602 --> 05:13.354
All:
Uhhh...

05:13.438 --> 05:14.897
Can't<i> you</i> do it?

05:14.981 --> 05:16.899
I can't do this alone.

05:16.983 --> 05:18.192
That monster
got this big

05:18.276 --> 05:19.360
because you kids
never helped

05:19.444 --> 05:22.196
keep the school clean,
like I asked.

05:22.280 --> 05:23.614
Fi-i-ne.

05:23.698 --> 05:26.034
Oh. What about these
water guns?

05:26.117 --> 05:28.870
Fill 'em up with soap
and spray the monster away.

05:28.953 --> 05:30.705
They're for playing,
not cleaning.

05:30.788 --> 05:33.082
We gotta<i> scrub</i>
this mess.

05:33.166 --> 05:35.168
But like this is
way easier.

05:35.251 --> 05:37.587
-Spray the monster away!
-Let's teach the
monster a lesson.
-Later, monster.

05:37.670 --> 05:39.213
Are you coming,
Mr. Mergley?

05:39.297 --> 05:41.507
You kids
never listen.

05:41.591 --> 05:42.717
I quit.

05:42.800 --> 05:44.969
♪♪

05:45.053 --> 05:46.554
Okay.
Take care.

05:46.637 --> 05:48.806
♪♪

05:48.890 --> 05:50.892
Alright,
keep your eyes peeled.

05:50.975 --> 05:53.561
Hi, guys!
Whazzu-u-p?

05:53.644 --> 05:54.562
Aah!

05:54.645 --> 05:56.230
No!

05:56.314 --> 05:57.440
Ohhhh.

05:57.523 --> 05:58.733
Oops.
Sorry, Nevin.

05:58.816 --> 05:59.859
[ Roar ]
[ Clang ]

05:59.942 --> 06:01.402
Claudette:
The monster's close!

06:01.486 --> 06:03.029
Cool James:
Sorry 'bout that, Nevin.
Bleh.

06:03.112 --> 06:04.864
♪♪

06:04.947 --> 06:06.866
Hey!
Garbage breath!

06:06.949 --> 06:09.243
Rub-a-dub-dub.

06:09.327 --> 06:10.953
Aaaaaaah!

06:11.037 --> 06:12.663
Aaaaah!

06:12.747 --> 06:13.915
It's working!

06:13.998 --> 06:17.335
♪♪

06:17.418 --> 06:18.503
Whoo-hoo!

06:18.586 --> 06:20.379
Yeah! We did it!
Great job, friends!

06:20.463 --> 06:21.923
Who's gonna clean up
<i>this</i> mess?

06:22.006 --> 06:23.841
The school will hire
another custodian.

06:23.925 --> 06:25.718
Don't worry.
Let's go back to class

06:25.802 --> 06:28.179
and just let everyone know
we saved their lives.

06:28.262 --> 06:29.430
[ Grumbling ]

06:29.514 --> 06:31.140
[ Roaring ]

06:31.224 --> 06:32.934
It's<i> ali-i-i-ve!</i>

06:33.017 --> 06:34.310
Soap 'im.

06:34.393 --> 06:35.561
I'm out!

06:35.645 --> 06:37.105
[ Roaring ]

06:37.188 --> 06:38.022
Aah!

06:38.106 --> 06:39.398
Cool James!

06:39.482 --> 06:40.525
Can't move.

06:40.608 --> 06:42.860
Trash...
too stinky.

06:42.944 --> 06:44.237
Both:
Aaah!

06:44.320 --> 06:46.906
Hey, monster,
snack on<i> this.</i>

06:46.989 --> 06:49.117
Huh?
[ Growl ]

06:49.200 --> 06:50.118
I gotcha.

06:50.201 --> 06:51.452
We need more supplies.

06:51.536 --> 06:53.621
♪♪

06:53.704 --> 06:54.747
Ha-chaaaa!
[ Screech! ]

06:54.831 --> 06:56.082
[ Slam ]

06:56.165 --> 06:57.625
All:
[ Gasp ]

06:57.708 --> 06:59.794
It's locked!

06:59.877 --> 07:01.003
Hey, there, Sethy.

07:01.087 --> 07:02.130
Just wanted
to circle back

07:02.213 --> 07:03.506
and see how things
were going

07:03.589 --> 07:05.633
with your locker
mess monster.

07:05.716 --> 07:07.844
Wait a minute.
Seth,<i> you</i> did this?

07:07.927 --> 07:09.720
Oh,<i> quelle surprise.</i>

07:09.804 --> 07:10.763
What, me?!

07:10.847 --> 07:12.849
No.
Commander Beefy did this!

07:12.932 --> 07:14.642
You're welcome,
by the way.

07:14.725 --> 07:17.728
[ Rumbling ]
[ Grumbling ]

07:17.812 --> 07:19.147
[ Roaring ]

07:19.230 --> 07:20.398
Oh, yeah!

07:20.481 --> 07:21.482
[ Lightning strikes ]

07:21.566 --> 07:24.443
[ Suspenseful music plays ]

07:24.527 --> 07:26.821
♪♪

07:26.904 --> 07:28.573
[ Buzzer ]
Yes!

07:28.656 --> 07:30.241
That is
truly repulsive.

07:30.324 --> 07:33.661
Commander Beefy,
how do we destroy that thing?!

07:33.744 --> 07:34.829
Well, let's see...

07:34.912 --> 07:35.955
You're going to need
to get all that

07:36.038 --> 07:37.665
magic space powder
off him.

07:37.748 --> 07:40.168
A good scrubbing
should do the trick,

07:40.251 --> 07:43.337
but it's gonna take a lot
for a monster that size.

07:43.421 --> 07:45.590
You'll help us,
right, Commander?

07:45.673 --> 07:47.175
I don't get
my hands dirty.

07:47.258 --> 07:48.759
But you're a team
of talented,

07:48.843 --> 07:51.053
creative thinkers,
and I just know

07:51.137 --> 07:52.638
you're gonna have
great success.

07:52.722 --> 07:54.348
Have fun with it.

07:54.432 --> 07:56.309
You couldn't just clean
your locker?

07:56.392 --> 07:58.144
You lazy little piggy.

07:58.227 --> 08:00.855
I was a lazy
little piggy boy.

08:00.938 --> 08:01.856
I'm sorry.

08:01.939 --> 08:03.608
We all could've been nicer

08:03.691 --> 08:04.692
to Mr. Mergley.

08:04.775 --> 08:06.444
Or tried harder
to help.

08:06.527 --> 08:07.486
Yes, yes.

08:07.570 --> 08:08.696
Plenty of blame
to go around.

08:08.779 --> 08:10.615
[ Growling ]

08:10.698 --> 08:12.992
If that crusty old Mergley
was here right now,

08:13.075 --> 08:15.536
I'd apologize
so sincerely to him.

08:15.620 --> 08:17.830
That's very sweet.

08:17.914 --> 08:18.956
Apology accepted.

08:19.040 --> 08:20.625
All:
Mr. Mergley!

08:20.708 --> 08:22.627
Have you...been here
this whole time?

08:22.710 --> 08:26.797
Yeah, I was just, you know,
hiding in the shadows.
[ Honk! ]

08:26.881 --> 08:28.716
Okay, kids, get ready.

08:28.799 --> 08:30.384
[ March plays ]

08:30.468 --> 08:32.220
Things are about to get messy.

08:32.303 --> 08:33.387
Huah!

08:33.471 --> 08:35.723
♪♪

08:35.806 --> 08:37.475
[ Rattle! ]
Ew!

08:37.558 --> 08:39.227
[ Grumble ]

08:39.310 --> 08:41.896
[ Suspenseful music plays ]

08:41.979 --> 08:43.022
[ Slurp! ]

08:43.105 --> 08:45.733
Let's scrub that big boy
in half!

08:45.816 --> 08:48.945
All:
Aaaaah!

08:49.028 --> 08:50.488
[ Screech! ]

08:50.571 --> 08:51.572
Aaah!

08:51.656 --> 08:53.574
Aaaaaaah!

08:53.658 --> 08:54.659
Hold on a sec.

08:54.742 --> 08:56.410
Aaaaaaah!

08:56.494 --> 08:58.412
Aah! Aah!

08:58.496 --> 09:00.998
♪♪

09:01.082 --> 09:03.376
It's not enough!
Huh?

09:03.459 --> 09:05.086
Uhhhh...
Uhhh...

09:05.169 --> 09:06.128
C'mon, Seth!

09:06.212 --> 09:08.422
Put a little elbow grease
into it.

09:08.506 --> 09:10.424
I'm having a really
tough time, okay?

09:10.508 --> 09:12.260
This thing
icks me out.

09:12.343 --> 09:14.053
Ugh!
-Seth, in life,

09:14.136 --> 09:15.596
there are no shortcuts.

09:15.680 --> 09:18.766
Sometimes you just gotta get
in there and get dirty.

09:18.849 --> 09:23.396
I see you, and I know you are
capable of great things.

09:23.479 --> 09:24.522
Whoa!

09:24.605 --> 09:26.357
All:
Mr. Mergley!

09:26.440 --> 09:27.858
[ Laughing ]

09:27.942 --> 09:29.068
What now?

09:29.151 --> 09:30.695
Oh, I'm
about to get dirty

09:30.778 --> 09:31.946
for Mergley.

09:32.029 --> 09:34.657
[ Panting ]
-♪ Cleanin' up my act ♪

09:34.740 --> 09:36.951
♪ It's time to put things back ♪

09:37.034 --> 09:39.996
♪ To how they were ♪

09:40.079 --> 09:43.916
-Ew!
-♪ Dirty world ♪

09:44.000 --> 09:45.376
♪ Cleanin' up my act ♪

09:45.459 --> 09:46.711
Yeah! Go, Seth!
Yeah, Seth, way to go!

09:46.794 --> 09:48.713
♪ It's time to put things back ♪

09:48.796 --> 09:49.714
♪ To how they were ♪

09:49.797 --> 09:50.798
<i>This</i> little piggy's

09:50.881 --> 09:52.133
gonna take<i> you...</i>

09:52.216 --> 09:54.176
to the cleaner's.
-♪ This dirty world ♪

09:54.260 --> 09:55.636
Aaaaah!

09:55.720 --> 09:58.306
♪ Nothing beats
some elbow grease ♪

09:58.389 --> 09:59.640
♪ To make it shine ♪
Dang.

09:59.724 --> 10:01.309
♪ Until it squeaks ♪

10:01.392 --> 10:03.519
♪ And clean until it's blown ♪

10:03.602 --> 10:07.481
♪ To smithereens ♪

10:07.565 --> 10:10.860
♪ Cleanin' up my act ♪

10:10.943 --> 10:12.111
Seth, you did it!

10:12.194 --> 10:14.822
You destroyed
the mess monster!

10:14.905 --> 10:17.158
Yeah, I guess I did,
didn't I?

10:17.241 --> 10:18.826
I get, now,
why Mergley wanted us

10:18.909 --> 10:20.578
to clean up
after ourselves.

10:20.661 --> 10:22.997
'Cause, if you don't
take care of messes,

10:23.080 --> 10:24.790
they can really get
out of control.

10:24.874 --> 10:27.084
It's just too bad
he got trashed.

10:27.168 --> 10:28.169
Yeah.

10:28.252 --> 10:31.422
[ Hollow ]
What, you guys miss me?

10:31.505 --> 10:32.840
All:
Mr. Mergley!

10:32.923 --> 10:33.841
You're alive!

10:33.924 --> 10:35.176
I'm not gone.

10:35.259 --> 10:36.427
Just really dirty.

10:36.510 --> 10:38.679
Seth, I heard
what you said,

10:38.763 --> 10:40.139
and I'm touched.

10:40.222 --> 10:42.516
I have something
for you.

10:42.600 --> 10:43.976
Oh, yeah,
y-your birthday

10:44.060 --> 10:45.353
punishment coupon,
right.

10:45.436 --> 10:47.688
Because you caused
this whole mess,

10:47.772 --> 10:50.775
now,<i> you're</i> going to help
me clean it all up.

10:50.858 --> 10:52.026
You know what, Mergley?

10:52.109 --> 10:53.319
You keep your pass.

10:53.402 --> 10:55.488
I<i> want</i>
to help you clean.

10:55.571 --> 10:57.198
In that case...

10:57.281 --> 10:58.699
<i>you</i> gotta help,
too!

10:58.783 --> 11:00.868
Grea-ea-t.
Thanks a lot, Seth.

11:00.951 --> 11:03.037
And you couldn't give it
to Cool James...

11:03.120 --> 11:04.038
Welp, good luck.

11:04.121 --> 11:05.373
I'm going home.

11:05.456 --> 11:14.673
♪♪

11:14.757 --> 11:17.927
♪♪

11:18.010 --> 11:20.262
Oh, yeah!
